Project Description
This is a Windows 10 WPF App to manage your Parse.com apps with a windows client.

This project is a client applicaton for PARSE.COM. You are able to connect to different parse.com apps with id and .net key. You can add classes and connect items with each other.


You can edit an item if you select one. You can also add properties on right side.
